<hr><A NAME = "1"><p id="main"><font size="5">Research Interests</font></a></p>

<p id="main"><font size="4">
My primary research is in the area of <b>natural language processing (NLP)</b> where our
  goal is to develop algorithms and systems
  that will vastly improve a user's ability to find, absorb, and extract
  information from on-line text.  My group's research generally proceeds
  at two complementary levels: we focus both on building real systems
  for large-scale natural language processing tasks and on developing
  techniques to address underlying theoretical problems in the
  syntactic, semantic and pragmatic analysis of natural language.  We rely on machine
  learning techniques including neural networks as our primary modeling tool, 
  both for guiding natural language system development and for exploring the mechanisms
  that underlie language understanding.</font>
</p>


